  "title": "Aerospace Technician | 1 year contract | Seletar Aerospace",
  "description": "<p>We're hiring a hands-on Technical Support Technician to join a high-performing team and contribute directly to production quality, process improvement, and new product launches.</p>\n<h3>🔑 Key Responsibilities</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide day-to-day technical support to production, ensuring optimal product performance and quality.</li>\n  <li>Manage product definition and evolution, working closely with IPT (Integrated Product Team).</li>\n  <li>Lead root cause analysis and implement quality improvement activities (8D, FTQP).</li>\n  <li>Coordinate new product introductions and support customer return investigations.</li>\n  <li>Drive continuous improvement initiatives (Kaizen) and maintain key KPIs (R1, FPY).</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with Design Authority and cross-functional teams across departments.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>🎁 Perks &amp; Benefits</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>💼 Contract Type: 1 year contract</li>\n  <li>💰 Completion Bonus: Negotiable, based on performance</li>\n  <li>⏰ Working Hours: Monday – Friday, 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>✅ Requirements</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>NITEC / Higher NITEC / Diploma in Engineering</li>\n  <li>1–5 years of relevant hands-on experience in a manufacturing or technical support environment</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you’re ready to make an impact and grow in a fast-paced, quality-driven environment — we want to hear from you!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>📞 Contact: 9186 0276<br>\n👩‍💼 Consultant: Ho Yu Qing Deborah (R1104551)<br>\n📌 Crew by HRnet | HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd | EA License: 24C2435</p>",
